								<dd>Оценки сообщений: 1050 <img src="images/reputation/pos.gif" title="" alt="" /><img src="images/reputation/pos.gif" title="" alt="" /><img src="images/reputation/pos.gif" title="" alt="" /><img src="images/reputation/pos.gif" title="" alt="" /><img src="images/reputation/pos.gif" title="" alt="" /><img src="images/reputation/pos.gif" title="" alt="" /></dd>
							                
